      <p>Fineguide may identify the client as a user of its services without implying any endorsement. Use of the client's brand assets will comply with any reasonable brand usage guidelines provided.</p>
      <p>If the client objects to such use, it must notify Fineguide in writing at <a href="mailto:office@fineguide.ai">office@fineguide.ai</a>. In the absence of such notice, the right to reference the client will be considered granted.</p>

      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <p>Don't hesitate to contact us if you have any questions.</p>
      <p>Via Email: <a href="mailto:office@fineguide.ai">office@fineguide.ai</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer t={t} lang={lang} />
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose-legal {
    color: var(--color-muted);
    line-height: 1.75;
  }
  .prose-legal h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-foreground);
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .prose-legal h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-foreground);
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .prose-legal h4 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-foreground);
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .prose-legal p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .prose-legal ul {
    list-style-type: disc;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .prose-legal ul li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .prose-legal strong {
    color: var(--color-foreground);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .prose-legal a {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }
  .prose-legal a:hover {
    opacity: 0.8;
  }
</style>
